        <div id="comment188904_show" class="single_comment">
          "the more I talk the less likely they are to actually get done"<br />&#10;There is a name for this psychological effect, but it won't come to me.<br />&#10;Basically, if you share a goal such as a New years Resolution, you get satisfaction from the sharing (which would normally be reserved for achieving said goal), and since you already have said satisfaction, you are less likely to follow through. 
        </div>
